{{Serbs}}

'''Serbs in Finland''' are an ethnic minority, mostly concentrated in [[Helsinki]]. According to estimates in 2007, there are approximately four thousand Serbs living permanently in Finland. The number of Finns of Serbian descent is unknown.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pxnet2.stat.fi/PXWeb/sq/584bcf95-8374-4b46-968c-09232d52764e |title=Table: Population 31.12. by Region, Language and Year (1990 - 2015) |publisher=PX-Web Statfin |date= |accessdate=2017-03-07 }}</ref>
